#: ../../source/vuln/ssti.rst:2
msgid "模版注入"
msgstr "Template Injection"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssti.rst:5
msgid "简介"
msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/vuln/ssti.rst:6
msgid "模板引擎用于使用动态数据呈现内容。此上下文数据通常由用户控制并由模板进行格式化，以生成网页、电子邮件等。模板引擎通过使用代码构造（如条件语句、循环等）处理上下文数据，允许在模板中使用强大的语言表达式，以呈现动态内容。如果攻击者能够控制要呈现的模板，则他们将能够注入可暴露上下文数据，甚至在服务器上运行任意命令的表达式。"
msgstr "Template engines are used to render content with dynamic data. This context data is often user-controlled and is formatted by templates to generate web pages, emails, and other output. Template engines process context data with code constructs such as conditionals and loops, allowing powerful language expressions inside templates to render dynamic content. If an attacker can control the template being rendered, they can inject expressions that expose context data or even execute arbitrary commands on the server."

